{"tid":1046809,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報復孟晚舟案 中國指控加國公民涉竊取刺探國家秘密","createTime":"2019-03-04T13:36:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T15:14:15.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5d08be423242feeed65d17059b8036ea06bd6a53","tid":1046809,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國與加拿大因華為孟晚舟引渡案而關係緊張，中國為報復加國，以涉嫌國安為由拘留了2名加國公民，中國政府今（4）日指控，其中一名被捕者、加國前外交官康明凱（Michael Kovrig）涉嫌竊取、刺探國家秘密和情報。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpkCljs3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpkCljs3.jpg&h=899ee637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國政府今（4）日指控，被捕的加國前外交官康明凱（Michael Kovrig）涉嫌竊取、刺探國家秘密和情報。（美聯社）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php2XoSFW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php2XoSFW.jpg&h=47087673&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國政府稱，被拘捕的加國商人史派佛（Michael Spavor），是康明凱的重要情報關係人，向康明凱提供情報。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n中國共產黨中央政法委新聞網站官方微博「中國長安網」今晚間發文稱，從有關部門獲悉，「康明凱竊取、刺探國家秘密和情報案偵辦工作已取得重要進展」。中國政府指控，康明凱自2017年以來，經常持普通護照和商務護照入境，「通過中國境內的關係人，竊取、刺探中國敏感信息和情報」。<br />\n<br />\n中國政府稱，另一名被拘捕的加國商人史派佛（Michael Spavor），是康明凱的重要情報關係人，向康明凱提供情報。「康的行為涉嫌為境外竊取、刺探國家秘密和情報，已嚴重觸犯了中國法律」。<br />\n<br />\n中國政府強調，其是法治國家，將會「嚴格依法辦案、文明辦案，充分保障康明凱及邁克爾的各項合法權利，依法安排領事探視等相關事宜。辦案部門將根據案件辦理情況，適時啟動下一步司法程序。」<br />\n<br />\n另據港媒指出，中國外交部今日例行記者會上，有記者問到，孟晚舟起訴加國侵犯她的憲法權利，中國卻不允許康明凱和史派佛會見律師，質疑是「雙重標準」。外交部發言人陸慷未正面回應，稱中方嚴格履行《中加領事協定》的義務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2716152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2716152&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4CvUjXV925tPaxuyg6D%2B4Js%3D&h=a469ab77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2716152&h=6433f9bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2716152</a>"},{"pid":"bf0071bd33ab960f50765fa86e66edc60026c4c3","tid":1046809,"uid":18569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:41:35.000Z","msg":"玩埋啲小手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228464aa92fd17bc335bacefab66cd059cc41acd","tid":1046809,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T13:43:50.000Z","msg":"又會咁岩美加佬搞慢慢周果日,調查突然有重大進展既?<br />\n<br />\n同埋精既就唔好去支那呀,果日貿易團咪醒水lo,臨時取消行程即閃返加拿大"},{"pid":"30086722d42a302363dcebddf70b94fb5879f65e","tid":1046809,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:05:36.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"4e9ef8d6e009ac356d0a29dde9d37568646d29cd","tid":1046809,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:09:17.000Z","msg":"擺明係報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雜種真係唔撚識國際關係架喎<br />\n我係加拿大就排支"},{"pid":"b5665118ff1f7eb4f0ff1044e1598462927e62d5","tid":1046809,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T14:13:06.000Z","msg":"去偷返自己被人偷左既野?"},{"pid":"0b4d3ddf4cff747bf219fa86e267f5b09facba19","tid":1046809,"uid":78143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/230336_2864d11df659194eaccee61298fe0fbd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F230336_2864d11df659194eaccee61298fe0fbd.gif&h=2665a912&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6624e562d11005a28790ca29ecefb30d0e5da994","tid":1046809,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:05:36.000Z","msg":"為國捐軀啦今鋪"},{"pid":"afe58f3c5deefc479d462a7cc7c41cd5e7757553","tid":1046809,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T15:13:28.000Z","msg":"港共政府仲唔跟隨主子<br />\n捉尻啲加拿人去告<img src=\"/assets/faces